<figureCitation id="132ADB98FF8FFF8BFE8FFBF7FE9EFB36" box="[276,349,1147,1171]" captionStart="FIGURES 32–37" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1970,1993]" captionTargetBox="[168,1433,275,1853]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,249,1899]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 32–37. Male genitalia of Sophonia similis sp. nov. 32. Genital capsule, lateral view; 33. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 34.Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view; 36. Aedeagus, lateral view; 37.Aedeagus posteroventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1170021/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="360">32–37</figureCitation>
